# MastraClaw — Layer A bootstrap env vars
#
# These are the ONLY env vars MastraClaw reads. Everything else (LLM provider
# keys, ElevenLabs, Telegram bot tokens, MCP auth, …) lives in Supabase Vault
# and is configured per-user via the in-app setup wizard.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values from the Supabase
# dashboard (Project Settings → Database / API / Storage).
#
# Public-vs-secret split:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_*           ← exposed to the browser bundle. ONLY for keys
#                              that Supabase explicitly documents as public
#                              (URL + publishable key).
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
#   DATABASE_URL,
#   DATABASE_SSL,
#   SUPABASE_S3_*           ← server-only. NEVER prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC_.

# === Public (browser-safe) Supabase config ===
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# === Server-only Supabase secrets ===
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
DATABASE_URL=
DATABASE_SSL=true

# === Optional: Supabase Storage / S3 ===
# SUPABASE_S3_ENDPOINT=https://<REF>.supabase.co/storage/v1/s3
# SUPABASE_S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# SUPABASE_S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=

# === Optional model defaults (override via stored agent config) ===
# MAIN_AGENT_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5
# SPECIALIST_MODEL=anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5

# === ElevenLabs voice defaults ===
#
# Voice ID and model ID are intentionally hard-coded as env defaults so
# every deployment ships with a working voice configuration. The values
# below are the SHIFT/MastraClaw default voice — change them per
# deployment if a different brand voice is needed.
#
# An admin CAN override these from the future settings page (writes to
# app_settings.elevenlabs.voice_id_override / model_id_override). The
# loading order at runtime is:
#
#     1. app_settings override (if set by admin)   -- highest priority
#     2. process.env value (this file)
#     3. fail loud
#
# The ElevenLabs API key itself is NOT in env — it lives in Vault as
# `app:elevenlabs_api_key` and is set during the Admin Setup wizard.
ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=rKiu7lQ4c5P3az3745s3
ELEVENLABS_MODEL_ID=eleven_v3
